| History                 = The Undertow were a terrorist organization led by the creature [[Protocol (Earth-616)|Protocol]]. They implanted devices in their superhuman operatives the [[Soldiers of Misfortune (Earth-616)|Soldiers of Misfortune]] to control their actions.

Namorita was press ganged into serving the Undertow as their agent Hard for many months until she was freed by Night Thrasher. Cardinal's ex-girlfriend Sparrow was also forced into service...it is unclear if she or the other agents were ever freed from the control of the Undertow.{{Citation}}
